00:39:54.870 --> 00:39:57.690
where people can Skype
their legal questions

00:39:57.690 --> 00:40:00.960
to an in-house lawyer who's
willing to say; I mean,

00:40:00.960 --> 00:40:03.720
it's very easy to get a lawyer
to say I'll commit an hour

00:40:03.720 --> 00:40:07.030
or 2 hours to answer
basic legal questions.

00:40:07.030 --> 00:40:09.500
It's much tougher when you say
oh and by the way we want you

00:40:09.500 --> 00:40:12.140
