an hour-and-a-half and then,

00:40:12.140 --> 00:40:14.850
you know, battle traffic
to come back to the office.

00:40:14.850 --> 00:40:18.140
So, that's a perfect example
where we can use technology

00:40:18.140 --> 00:40:20.070
to address so much of this,

00:40:20.070 --> 00:40:25.130
as long as the homeless shelter
has a terminal and can utilize

00:40:25.130 --> 00:40:27.790
