can have a whole wealth

00:40:27.790 --> 00:40:29.950
of additional lawyers
who are more than happy

00:40:29.950 --> 00:40:33.590
to spend half an hour
answering questions,

00:40:33.590 --> 00:40:34.890
and what we've created

00:40:34.890 --> 00:40:37.650
in the homeless youth
space is a whole toolkit.

00:40:37.650 --> 00:40:40.280
We have one for Washington,
D.C., one for New York,

00:40:40.280 --> 00:40:42.490
one for Florida,
one for California,

00:40:42.490 --> 00:40:46.760
where any lawyer can get the
basic information they need,

00:40:46.760 --> 00:40:48.340
because we know the
questions of many

00:40:48.340 --> 00:40:51.950
