00:40:51.950 --> 00:40:53.250
How do I get back in school?

00:40:53.250 --> 00:40:54.660
I'm a runaway from foster care,

00:40:54.660 --> 00:40:56.560
I want to get my
high school degree.

00:40:56.560 --> 00:41:00.380
How do I get access to my birth
certificate, because I want

00:41:00.380 --> 00:41:01.990
to get a driver's
license and I'm

00:41:01.990 --> 00:41:05.020
in a foster care environment,
I don't know how to do that?

00:41:05.020 --> 00:41:07.470
How do I apply for
public benefits,

00:41:07.470 --> 00:41:09.780
because I believe I
meet the requirements?

00:41:09.780 --> 00:41:12.000
There are all kinds of
questions, but there's a lot

00:41:12.000 --> 00:41:14.410
of repetition, so these
toolkits we put together

00:41:14.410 --> 00:41:17.040
and they're also online.

00:41:17.040 --> 00:41:19.490
So, any lawyer sitting
in their office can say,

00:41:19.490 --> 00:41:21.820
oh birth certificate

00:41:21.820 --> 00:41:25.860
or eliminating a criminal
infraction, type it in,

00:41:25.860 --> 00:41:28.150
and they get all the information
they need right there

00:41:28.150 --> 00:41:32.230
to answer these basic questions
for these homeless youth.

