by reducing the stature
of the courts.

00:42:17.020 --> 00:42:18.320
&gt;&gt; Hilarie Bass: Right.

00:42:18.320 --> 00:42:24.600
&gt;&gt; One of the arguments that
is sometimes made in comparison

00:42:24.600 --> 00:42:30.010
