00:42:30.010 --> 00:42:34.310
of politics in selecting

00:42:34.310 --> 00:42:37.870
and appointing judges
in the United States.

00:42:37.870 --> 00:42:42.450
So, that's I think
something I wanted

00:42:42.450 --> 00:42:44.730
to hear your opinion about.

