is retracting, but those people

00:46:39.370 --> 00:46:42.970
who are prepared to go out
there and serve the public

00:46:42.970 --> 00:46:44.400
in all kinds of different ways,

00:46:44.400 --> 00:46:47.990
there will be an unlimited
opportunity for people

00:46:47.990 --> 00:46:52.690
who are prepared to do that.

