00:48:56.300 --> 00:49:00.820
So, not only are we an exemplary
American legal Collection,

00:49:00.820 --> 00:49:05.100
we are also a phenomenal
international foreign legal

00:49:05.100 --> 00:49:09.410
collection as well, but library,
as librarians even though many

00:49:09.410 --> 00:49:11.390
of our librarians
are JDs and MLS's,

