00:53:13.490 --> 00:53:17.630
of a period where good
health favors many of them

00:53:17.630 --> 00:53:20.400
and they have financial
resources.

00:53:20.400 --> 00:53:25.280
We don't seem to have
an organized method

00:53:25.280 --> 00:53:28.930
that could bring those
individuals into the fold

00:53:28.930 --> 00:53:31.400
to help staff some of the.

