that have spent 30-40
years in some cases ranging

00:53:53.160 --> 00:53:57.890
from small practitioners up
to the judiciary, so one piece

00:53:57.890 --> 00:54:01.010
for you is yes it's great
to talk about the technology

00:54:01.010 --> 00:54:04.260
and the application and the
rest of it, but the human talent

00:54:04.260 --> 00:54:07.220
that you have available to
you might be another piece.

