One question.

00:54:20.300 --> 00:54:22.820
&gt;&gt; Well, I've sat here and I've
heard president have asked,

00:54:22.820 --> 00:54:27.830
speak on the issues with
women and the legal profession

00:54:27.830 --> 00:54:30.110
and staying in the retention
of women legal profession,

00:54:30.110 --> 00:54:32.410
and then you've talked about
you have a task force that's

00:54:32.410 --> 00:54:34.910
studying that, but I'd
be curious if you're able

00:54:34.910 --> 00:54:39.270
to discuss or add any
perspective on what type

00:54:39.270 --> 00:54:40.570
of things you're seeing

00:54:40.570 --> 00:54:43.580
as to why women are leaving
the profession and not staying,

00:54:43.580 --> 00:54:48.610
in particular, especially with
the minority women and their,

00:54:48.610 --> 00:54:50.960
the greater gap and so I
would just be interested

00:54:50.960 --> 00:54:52.260
in hearing more from that.

00:54:52.260 --> 00:54:53.560
&gt;&gt; Hilarie Bass: Well, some

00:54:53.560 --> 00:54:54.860
of the consistent
responses we're getting

00:54:54.860 --> 00:54:57.290
and obviously don't come
to any direct conclusions,

